Insider Activity


Individual




Prady Iyyanki



Mr. Prady Iyyanki is on the Board of Directors at Forum Energy Technologies, Inc. Mr. Iyyanki was previously employed as Vice President by GE Oil & Gas, Inc., President & CEO-Turbomachinery Equipment by General Electric Co., and President & Chief Executive Officer by GE Jenbacher GmbH & Co. OG. He received his undergraduate degree from Jawaharlal Nehru Technological University and a graduate degree from South Dakota State University.



